<C>__{old lady}
<P>__{(screaming)}
<D>__{can't you read english? you illiterate foreign pig! you come here from your own filthy country and think you can mess our streets up! you should be fried alive, you dirty verminous ... etc. etc.}
<A>__{sam sees the trail of dossier litter blowing about the pavement. he lets go of jill for a moment to grab at the papers. the lady continues screaming at him, her little pekinese dog (who incidentally wears a plaster over his bum hole) yaps at his ankles, ripping sam's new trousers. sam is torn between trying to regain the pages of the dossier and following jill who has disappeared round the corner. he gives up retrieving the paper and rushes after}
